    "description": "Dookie Clicker is the most absurdly addictive game that unapologetically puts you in charge of a steaming pile of... well, you know. Your mission? Click the crap out of it and watch as your dookie evolves from a simple turd into a majestic, over-the-top, freak show of fecal artistry.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why Should You Give A Crap?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Push Harder:</strong> Upgrade your clicking power, passive income, and more to turn your dookie into a grotesque masterpiece that would make even the most seasoned toilet tremble. Finish it all with <strong>The Big Flush™️</strong> and then hit endless mode to complete your collection of skins.<br></li><li><strong>Polish a turd</strong>: We've made it possible. From jellies to precious metals, you can dress up your Dookie in a growing assortment of common, rare, and ultra rare skins, which are tradable and marketable.<br></li><li><strong>Disgustingly Addictive</strong>: It’s gross, it’s offensive, and it’s so satisfying that you won’t be able to stop yourself from going deeper down the toilet bowl.<br>Perfect for anyone who’s ever wanted to embrace the absolute absurdity of life and laugh in the face of decency. Because sometimes, you just want to revel in the ridiculous.</li></ul><br>Get ready to click the crap out of it— because if life’s a joke, this is the punchline you’ve been waiting for.",
